2.10	Pierre_Berge	Pierre Bergé	Pierre Bergé (born November 14, 1930) is a French industrialist and patron. He is perhaps best known as the co-founder of Yves Saint Laurent Couture House and former partner of fashion designer Yves Saint Laurent.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/BERGE_Pierre-24x30-1998b.jpg/220px-BERGE_Pierre-24x30-1998b.jpg
